    "documentation": "This schema (v14) introduces significant changes to accommodate the distinct sections (biography, research, publications, teaching, service, education, contact) present in the extracted content.  Each section now has its own object with a 'recent_updates' array.  Each item in 'recent_updates' is an object with a 'description' (string) and an optional 'url' (string, format: url).  The 'personal_info' section remains largely the same as in v13. An 'additional_notes' field is added to capture miscellaneous information.  This structure provides a more accurate and flexible representation of the data compared to the previous version."
